ergamon Press Inc. (1990):[6] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.[7] "Product Information. Torisel (temsirolimus)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories, Philadelphia, PA.', 1767369485);
